snippet: The deadline for enrollment under the Affordable Care Act is midnight Sunday, though applications still pending at that time should be acceptable.
abstract: Ann Carrns Your Money Adviser column cautions window for enrolling in Affordable Care Act's health insurance is closing; notes that as deadline nears, traffic on government website Healthcare.gov is increasing; warns remaining without coverage will most likely result in penalty.
lead_paragraph: The deadline for enrollment under the Affordable Care Act is midnight Sunday, though applications still pending at that time should be acceptable.
